employees, including Mickey Jannol and Shih-Ling Tu, right. ROBERT DURELL; 
Photo, Jeweler Erik Laykin helps Jennie Kim at I. Magnin downtown store. Laykin 
is studying Korean to communicate with customers. LACY ATKINS / Los Angeles 
