<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA063089-0145 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 76742 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
June 30, 1989, Friday, Southland Edition 
</P>
