(top) after making a wild pitch, but it's too late as plate umpire Terry Tata 
calls the play Thursday night. ; Photo, Dodger shortstop Alfredo Griffin forces 
out Padre Jack Clark during the second inning Thursday night at Dodger Stadium. 
